name: GRR Rapid Response
description: This app implements various investigative actions from the GRR API

actions.description: Validate the asset configuration for connectivity using supplied configuration
List all the connections configured on the device
List all the endpoints/sensors configured on the device
Look for files matching given criteria
Retrieve matching regex in a client's browser cache

users.description: Users to query. Use commas to separate

count.description: Max number of items to fetch

created_by.description: Only return hunts created by a given user. If approved_by or/and description_contains are also supplied, then logical AND is applied to all the criteria. NOTE: This filter can only be used in conjunction with the 'active_within' filter (to prevent queries of death)

description_contains.description: Only return hunts where description contains given substring (matching is case-insensitive). If created_by or/and approved_by are also supplied, then logical AND is applied to all the criteria. NOTE: This filter can only be used in conjunction with the 'active_within' filter (to prevent queries of death)

active_within.description: Only return hunts that were active within given time duration

count.description: Max number of items to fetch
